Package Application.Controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutController
    Controller class for managing the page containing the information about the platform and the useful contacts.
    ErrorController
    Controller class for managing the page that displays the Application.Exception.
    FeedController
    Controller class for managing the page with all the Vision(s).
    FeelingController
    Controller class for managing the page in which the User(s) express their Feeling(s).
    InDepthController
    Controller class for managing the In-depth Match(es).
    IndexController
    Controller class for managing the home page of the platform.
    LoginController
    Controller class for managing the login of the User(s) of the platform.
    MatchController
    Controller class for managing the Quick Match(es).
    ProfileController
    Controller class for viewing and managing a User's profile.
    QuizController
    Controller class for viewing, answering and recording the answers to Quizzes.
    ScenarioController
    Controller class for viewing Scenarios and their data.
    StatisticsController
    Controller class for retrieving and formatting statistics data.
    UserInfoController
    Controller class for managing User information.
    VisionController
    Controller class for managing Visions.
